# Proactive functional suggestions

- When user asks for admin, operations, or bot UX changes, always propose 2-4 adjacent useful features.
- Prioritize suggestions that reduce manual work: metrics, audit log, safe delete, filters, bulk actions.
- If a feature improves testability, explicitly suggest it (seed data, e2e checklist, debug command).
- Keep suggestions short and practical, with clear "why it helps now".
- Do not block implementation; implement requested change first, then suggest extras.

